== Reaction Formula ==
* With identifiers:
** 8 [[PROTON]][c] '''+''' 6 [[Reduced-ferredoxins]][c] '''+''' 1 [[NITRITE]][c] '''=>''' 1 [[AMMONIUM]][c] '''+''' 2 [[WATER]][c] '''+''' 6 [[Oxidized-ferredoxins]][c]
* With common name(s):
** 8 H+[c] '''+''' 6 a reduced ferredoxin [iron-sulfur] cluster[c] '''+''' 1 nitrite[c] '''=>''' 1 ammonium[c] '''+''' 2 H2O[c] '''+''' 6 an oxidized ferredoxin [iron-sulfur] cluster[c]

